{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plantasia is a cozy semi-idle, gardening &amp; puzzle game designed to sit at the bottom 1/3 of your screen so you can play in-between tasks without disrupting your work!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236330/extras/Nurture_plants.png?t=1731092915\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nurture Plants:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plant your seeds and watch them grow into beautiful blooms. Then, harvest them for materials and extra seeds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236330/extras/Combine_species.png?t=1731092915\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine Species:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use some of your seeds in the station lab to create hybrids, and grow new interesting plant types for better appearances and resource yields.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236330/extras/Seed_bundles.png?t=1731092915\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Create Seed Bundles:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The bundles will help you complete quests and acquire new blueprints to personalize your station!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236330/extras/Multitasking.png?t=1731092915\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make your space YOURS:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plantasia gives you plenty of opportunities to personalize the looks of your space station, making sure that you can make it as cozy as possible. After all, home is where the plants are.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multitasking:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plantasia is designed to encourage play during small breaks, without disrupting your regular workflow as you transition in and out of other tasks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Story mode:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If the world of Plantasia and its secrets call to you, it is also possible to engage with the optional campaign - where deeper, more serious truths about the world are revealed.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236330/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731092915","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236330/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1731092915","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236330/5d67fb0cb9986e2364421a75504f86065b8b2e0e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731092915","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236330/5d67fb0cb9986e2364421a75504f86065b8b2e0e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731092915","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Captions available","id":13}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plantasia is a cozy semi-idle, gardening &amp; puzzle game designed to sit at the bottom 1/3 of your screen so you can play in-between tasks without disrupting your work!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236330/extras/Nurture_plants.png?t=1731092915\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nurture Plants:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plant your seeds and watch them grow into beautiful blooms. Then, harvest them for materials and extra seeds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" 